snippet.title: Ubiquatopia - Battle gameplay test
snippet.description:
A quick gameplay showcase for the battle system in Ubiquatopia, an in-development strategy game where each action is a card.
If you want to check the game out (it's free), you can get it at: https://justacicada.itch.io/ubiquatopia
